name: NOVA SCOTIA PLANE SPOTTING! Halifax Stanfield International Airport (YHZ)
description:
Back in August, I spent a day of plane spotting at Halifax Stanfield International Airport - the busiest in Nova Scotia!

YHZ has some very solid traffic, ranging from Sable Aviation's BN-2 Islander all the way to heavies like Korean Air Cargo's 777F and Eurowings Discover's A330s.

Definitely an airport I'll come back to someday! But maybe with a proper ladder.
